Release binaries for Tasmota firmware 12.1.1 on ESP8266

Firmware for ESP8266 with easy configuration using webUI, OTA updates, automation using timers or rules, expandability and
entirely local control over MQTT, HTTP, Serial or KNX.

See RELEASE NOTES.

Find latest development binaries for Tasmota firmware at http://ota.tasmota.com/tasmota/.
Find release binaries for Tasmota firmware on ESP32 at http://ota.tasmota.com/tasmota32/release/.

For an initial installation of Tasmota use the webinstaller.

If you benefit from the Tasmota project please consider making a donation.



These binaries are built using core 2.7.4.9
